nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 145 is the 123rd issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 53rd published by Titan Magazines. It was released on October 22, 2013 and came with one of two sets of exclusive 2013 Topps Star Wars Illustrated: A New Hope trading cards from Topps and HighBridge Audio. In addition, it also included a chance to win a pre-release copy of the Death Star Owner's Technical Manual. It is also the first Insider issue to have behind the scenes notes on the creation of the Rogues Gallery article, supplied on the Facebook page "Star Wars Sourcebooks."

In Star Wars Insider, we'll be solving the riddle of Darth Vader. Is he the Star Wars saga's most dastardly villain, or its greatest hero? We'll be asking the experts. You'll never look at him the same way again!
